description: More than 600 people are arrested after tens of thousands attended a rally against the president.
title: Belarus Lukashenko: Hundreds arrested at mass protests in Minsk

maintext: "We finally feel like we matter because we've been living in apathy for way too long and now we just have this feeling of solidarity and we actually think that - well, I feel personally that - changes already are happening so that's definitely not the time to give up."
